"{\"uid\": \"tmz.com-2024-08-06-colin-jost-olympics-toe-injury-tahiti-reef\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Colin Jostis off the hook from his Olympics coverage duties in Tahiti after a week of injury drama, starting withhis toe wounds... which he quipped invite ants to move in if he stands still too long.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 63, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9949281167100166, \"rank\": 0.005097509978089003, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yep, things really went south for NBC's 2024 surfing correspondent since landing in French Polynesia -- it was injury after injury ... kickstarting with a nasty run-in with a coral reef last week, which left three of his toes wrapped in gauze.\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999919690960332, \"rank\": 7.137821132163185e-06, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 292, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9788382135672536, \"rank\": 0.021619288671476992, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do I have a joke?\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, I am here.\\\"\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Colin Jost gives an update on his staph-infected foot in his latest live shot with NBC Olympics Late Night host Maria Taylor.#SNL#Olympics2024Paris@MariaTaylorpic.twitter.com/KorNkozVYy  Colin had a good laugh about it, even joking his WikiFeet fame might take a hit.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colin Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Jost\"}, {\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Jane_Taylor\", \"score\": 0.6991000335024672, \"rank\": 0.4243081990491219, \"text\": \"Maria Taylor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Jane_Taylor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Jane_Taylor\"}, {\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saturday_Night_Live\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.120051255674371e-18, \"text\": \"SNL\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saturday_Night_Live\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saturday_Night_Live\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But right now, the only thing crashing the scene could be ants -- something he told NBC'sMaria Taylorhe never saw coming.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added he was practically a regular in the medical tent with all the injuries he's racked up -- he got a staph infection in his foot from the reef scrape ... and woke up with an unrelated ear infection.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All in all, Colin's been juggling 3 different meds since Toe-hiti Gate.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, in true \\\"SNL\\\" style, he hilariously managed to embrace his out-of-place vibe among the surfing athletes.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, in the end, Colin can not keep going with all these injuries.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A job's gotta get done, and Australian weathermanLuke Bradnamhas replaced him.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9457547618604508, \"rank\": 0.03388463258678366, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes!\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send me email updates and offers from TMZ and its Affiliates.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"score\": 0.9999996823162797, \"rank\": 3.1768377607011136e-07, \"text\": \"TMZ\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By subscribing, I agree to thePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Use\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": []}]}"